                             <p class="s-post-text">
                                 A Web Developer is a computer programmer who can read and write code in a variety of programming languages. Web Developers focus specifically on building web applications over HTTP using the client server model. They often extend and customize the features of content management systems such as WordPress.
                             </p>
                         </div>

