                             <h2 class="s-post-subtitle">What is a Web Designer?</h2>
                             <p class="s-post-text">
                                 A Web Designer’s primary role is to create aesthetically pleasing visual designs to implement on a website. While Web Designers often have some knowledge of front end technologies such as HTML and CSS, they are primarily concerned with the look and feel rather than the mechanics of the web application.
                             </p>
                         </div>

