                                 While I am not a designer by training, I have a good eye for functional and practical web design. I designed this custom WordPress theme entirely on my own. The theme’s source files include standard WordPress templates as defined in their template hierarchy as well as custom PHP classes to effectively organize the theme’s resources and apply any necessary business logic. It also implements security precautions and best practices as outlined in the WordPress codex.
                             </p>
